stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unauthenticated
    
    Unauthenticated --> SignInPage: navigate /admin
    SignInPage --> GoogleOAuth: click "Sign in with Google"
    
    GoogleOAuth --> GoogleConsent: user consent
    GoogleConsent --> CallbackHandler: redirect to /sign-in/callback
    
    CallbackHandler --> CreateSession: validate OAuth token
    CreateSession --> Authenticated: JWT created
    
    Authenticated --> AdminPanel: redirect /admin
    AdminPanel --> [*]
    
    GoogleOAuth --> SignInPage: cancel
    CreateSession --> SignInPage: invalid token
